{"tid":1267671,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"記住：只要 9月25日夠 18 歲，就可以現在登記選民","createTime":"2019-06-30T04:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T18:05:59.000Z","uid":197872,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3958e7fc5f8d9c27e3edb29002906aa8667dfa15","tid":1267671,"uid":197872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/faq.html#9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ffaq.html%239&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=6d57ec8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/faq.html#9</a><br />\n<br />\n問九 : 我在2019年9月底才滿十八歲，而 2019年的選民新登記限期則是 7月 2日，我現在可不可以先登記做選民？<br />\n答九 : 2019年正式選民登記冊將在2019年9月25日或之前發表。若你在該日期或之前年滿十八歲，又是香港永久性居民，就符合資格，現在已可以申請登記做選民。"},{"pid":"aafdfb30dca9a490d2987b478076342368fd6872","tid":1267671,"uid":18350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"推比00後睇"},{"pid":"1b4e7e085492fd0b02a136d7f068d96f70dbd3b5","tid":1267671,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cffecd2e1c0b6d9b4123b333d4842e172ed50143","tid":1267671,"uid":221265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">SORRY借個位：<br />\n<br />\n【廣傳有圖】認住依班賣港青年 好怕佢哋扮素人中立派空降區選 ！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267678</a></span>"},{"pid":"6387c09f73ad309ef658e1d188a8c77e9c9019e7","tid":1267671,"uid":247774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:30:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6550550f142541874f08811971a6a0ece06ba380","tid":1267671,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"<i